    <div class="hero-container">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">About Us</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">A publication for the curious and creative</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">We're building a community of thinkers, makers, and explorers who believe in the power of ideas to shape the future.</p>
    </div>
